# LXD/LXC

## config
lxd init


### storage
lxc storage list
lxc storage edit remote

### network
lxc set network.ovn.nothbound_connection tcp:172.17.32.8:6641,tcp:172.17.32.9:6641,tcp:172.17.32.5:6641
lxc network list
lxc network create default --type ovn
lxc profile device add default eth0 nic network=default name=eth0


### cluster
lxc cluster list

node-01> lxc cluster add <node-02>  ## generate token for node-02

node-02> lxd init ## use token when ask to join cluster

lxc cluster edit <node-02>

## join a cluster, using a password
node-03> lxc remote add cluster <node-01>
## join a cluster, using cert
node-03> cat snap/lxd/common/config/client.crt

#### Copy cert to node-01 file client-node-03.crt, and add
node-01> lxc config trust add client-node-03.crt
node-03> lxc remote add cluster <node-01> # join
node-03> lxc remote switch cluster # switch client from local to cluster


### images
lxc config set images.default_architecture=x86_64



